---
---
<section class="py-24 border-b border-b1" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-10">
    <span class="inline-block text-[11px] font-bold tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-accent mb-2.5">How it works</span>
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-t1 leading-[1.15] mb-3">Calculating overtime pay</h2>
    <p class="text-[15px] text-t2 max-w-[600px] leading-[1.7] mb-10">The math is simple once you know your state's threshold and multiplier. Here's the full breakdown.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-start">
      <!-- Left Column: Steps -->
      <div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-[36px_1fr] gap-4 items-start">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-s2 border border-b1 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold text-t1 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-t1 mb-1.5 tracking-tight">Find your overtime rate</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-t2 leading-relaxed">Multiply your regular hourly rate by the overtime multiplier. US federal default is <strong>1.5× (time and a half)</strong>. Example: $15.00 × 1.5 = $22.50/hr overtime rate.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-[36px_1fr] gap-4 items-start">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-s2 border border-b1 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold text-t1 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-t1 mb-1.5 tracking-tight">Multiply by overtime hours</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-t2 leading-relaxed">Take your overtime rate and multiply by hours worked past the threshold. Example: $22.50/hr × 8 OT hours = <strong class="text-green">$180 overtime pay</strong>.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-[36px_1fr] gap-4 items-start">
            <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-s2 border border-b1 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold text-t1 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-t1 mb-1.5 tracking-tight">Add your regular pay</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-t2 leading-relaxed">Regular pay = 40 hours × base rate. Add both for your total gross. Example: $600 regular + $180 overtime = <strong class="text-accent font-bold">$780 total</strong>.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column: Formulas & Qualifications -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <!-- Static Formula Card -->
        <div class="bg-bg border border-b1 rounded-2xl p-6 shadow-sm flex flex-col gap-4">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold text-t1 tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-4 h-4 text-accent">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 15.75V18m-3-3.675v3.675m-3-3v3M3.375 7.5h17.25c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125v-1.5c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125H3.375c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v1.5c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125z" />
            </svg>
            Overtime Pay Formula
          </h3>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
            <!-- Step 1 Formula -->
            <div class="bg-s2 border border-b1 rounded-xl p-3.5 flex flex-col gap-2">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-t3 uppercase tracking-[0.05em]">1. Overtime Rate</span>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-t2 font-medium flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg border border-b1 rounded-lg text-t1 font-bold shadow-xs">Regular Hourly Rate</span>
                <span>×</span>
                <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg border border-b1 rounded-lg text-t1 font-bold shadow-xs">Multiplier (e.g. 1.5x)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Step 2 Formula -->
            <div class="bg-s2 border border-b1 rounded-xl p-3.5 flex flex-col gap-2">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-t3 uppercase tracking-[0.05em]">2. Overtime Pay</span>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-t2 font-medium flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg border border-b1 rounded-lg text-t1 font-bold shadow-xs">Overtime Rate</span>
                <span>×</span>
                <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg border border-b1 rounded-lg text-t1 font-bold shadow-xs">Overtime Hours Worked</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Step 3 Formula -->
            <div class="bg-s2 border border-b1 rounded-xl p-3.5 flex flex-col gap-2">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-t3 uppercase tracking-[0.05em]">3. Total Weekly Pay</span>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs text-t2 font-medium flex-wrap">
                <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg border border-b1 rounded-lg text-t1 font-bold shadow-xs">Regular Pay (up to 40h)</span>
                <span>+</span>
                <span class="px-2.5 py-1 bg-bg border border-b1 rounded-lg text-green font-bold shadow-xs">Overtime Pay</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
